Introduction

Q6IX (Korean: 큐빅스; Japanese: キュービックス) is a three-member girl group under Retro Entertainment. They made their debut as a duo on December 23, 2019 with the single "한번더화이트크리스마스".

On December 15, 2022, they shared that Yeonjeong and Jaeeun had left the group and terminated their contracts due to academic work.
